== Romanian ==
===Etymology===
The official DEX cites either a Latin origin from unattested ''*[[flutulus]]'', or a pre-Roman origin. The Romanian word has an Albanian [[cognate]], ''[[fluturë]]''.
===Noun===
'''fluture''' pl ''[[fluturi]]''
#A [[butterfly]].

